    <tags>obs obs-websocket obs-studio streaming broadcasting cli</tags>
    <summary>A command line interface for controlling OBS Studio via the obs-websocket protocol.</summary>
    <description>A CLI tool for controlling OBS Studio with shell commands via the obs-websocket protocol.

Features:
- Scene management (list, switch, get current)
- Input control (mute, volume, audio settings)
- Stream control (start, stop, toggle)
- Recording control (start, stop, pause, resume)
- Filter management
- Transition control
- Event listening and monitoring
- Virtual camera control
- Replay buffer management

Installation requires OBS Studio with obs-websocket plugin enabled.</description>
    <releaseNotes>https://github.com/cdavis-code/obs_websocket/blob/main/packages/obs_cli/CHANGELOG.md</releaseNotes>
